docs.summary: A WixForms element displays customizable forms and collects all the info that site visitor entered into the form fields.

params.name: formValues
params.doc: A data object that is passed to the event handler.

docs.summary:
Sets form field values.
> **Note:**
> The WixForms element is only available in Wix Studio.
description: The `setFieldValues()` function sets field values in a form.
Setting the invalid field values fires a `onFieldValuesChange` event. The event returns fields with previous valid values.

docs.summary: An object containing information about an input field in a form.

members.name: keyvalue
members.doc: Key is the form field name, and value is the data submitted for the given field.
